data.description: Welcome to 105 Athena Way in Jarrell – a captivating 2-story haven that redefines modern living. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this stylish abode is a blend of luxury and functionality. The gourmet kitchen, sleek living areas, and spacious bedrooms provide comfort at every turn. Step outside to a generous backyard, ready for your personal touch. Priced at $315,000, this is your chance to own a piece of elevated living. Don't miss out – make 105 Athena Way your new address today!
